  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">500 families in Bolivia need your help</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Micani, the most poverty-stricken town in Bolivia, is in great need. They have been using old methods of cooking, old bathrooms or none, and outdated contaminated water management. As a result, there are many diseases that are caused by smoke pollution, drinking dirty water, and lack of hand washing. Today we are already working in 19 communities of Micani with 412 families. With your help, a total of 43 communities could potentially be a part of this development in the future.</narrative>
  </description>
